# 🏎️ Pixel Racer

A top-down pixel-styled racing game built with Phaser 3.

## 🎮 How to Play

- **UP Arrow or W** - Accelerate
- **DOWN Arrow or S** - Brake
- **LEFT Arrow or A** - Turn Left
- **RIGHT Arrow or D** - Turn Right

## 🚀 Play Online

Visit the GitHub Pages link to play (coming soon!)

## 📦 Features

- Top-down racing gameplay
- Smooth car physics
- Speed indicator
- Boundary collision detection

